{
  "stem": "3331.3",
  "chunk_idx": 15,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They didn't want to leave anything, so we took a path, house by house, the ghetto where we lived for 300 years.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It took us about three months.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Meanwhile, after two weeks, all Rzeszow was liquidated by actions to Belzec.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They made four akcja.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The first action was 12,000 [?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Jews. ?]",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Akcja, we used to call akcja.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a day when they said, today is a liquidation.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This was called an 'akcja.' It's 'action.'",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So there were four akcjas.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The first akcja, they took 12,000 Jews from Rzeszow. 6,000 were loaded on trains, on cattle cars, and they brought them to Belzec.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "6,000 Were taken to a-- to a forest in Glogow, not far from Kolbuszowa, where ditches-- holes-- were dug the day before, and they shot all the people.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they shot them-- half of them were not killed.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They fell in, and the people on top of it, people on top of it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they killed 6,000 in this day.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Later, when we were in the woods, one joined us-- a man who was one of the people who fell in, but he was not killed.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it took him four days to come out of this hole where he was covered with people.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "After four days, naked he came out, and he came to our group in the woods.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Well, this was, in Rzeszow, four actions.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They liquidated--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, we were-- we were-- when I was in Kolbuszowa, destroying the houses.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My-- when my mother was taken away-- this was the 7th of July-- she somehow gave to somebody a letter.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, you ask, why did I survive?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Somebody survived.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Somebody survived-- he had a legacy what gave him the strength to survive.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Otherwise, nobody could survive.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
